洛杉矶宣布进入紧急状态。
Los Angeles declared a state of emergency.
来源：推特（本文持续更新中。
Source: Twitter (this article is continuously updated.
文中段首所示时间为本文更新时间。
The time shown at the beginning of the middle paragraph is for this article.
）意大利0800【新增587例确诊病例，累计确诊3089例】根据当地时间3月4日18时意大利卫生部公布的最近数据，现有患者2706例，死亡107例。
Italy 0800 [new 587 confirmed cases, cumulative confirmed 3089 cases] According to the latest data released by the Italian Ministry of Health on March 4, 1800 local time, there are now 2,706 cases and 107 deaths.
较3月3日18时新增587例，新增28例死亡病例。
There were 587 new cases and 28 new deaths since 18: 00 on March 3.
累计确诊总人数为3089。
The cumulative total number of confirmed cases is 3089.
意大利卫生部4日宣布，自3日以来，民防部门已经向疫情“红区”（伦巴第的十个城镇及威尼托的一个城镇）的居民分发了2.5万支医用口罩。
The Ministry of Health announced Thursday that since March 3, civil defense authorities have distributed 25,000 medical masks to residents of the "red zone" of the outbreak, 10 towns in Lombardy and a town in Veneto.
同时，还向意大利全境的医护人员提供了40万个FFP2和FFP3两个欧洲标准等级的防护口罩。
At the same time, 400,000 FFP2 and FFP3 European standard level face masks were provided to medical personnel throughout Italy.
巴西0800【巴西确诊3例疑似病例数量跃升至531例】当地时间3月4日，巴西卫生部长路易斯·曼德塔（Luis Mandetta）召开发布会并表示，截至4日下午17时，巴西再新确诊1例新冠肺炎病例，患者是一名居住在圣保罗市的46岁哥伦比亚男性，最近曾到访西班牙、意大利、奥地利和德国，返回圣保罗出现症状后就医。
Brazil 0800 The number of suspected cases jumped to 531 on March 4, Brazilian Health Minister Luis Mandetta said at 17: 00 pm Thursday that a 46-year-old Colombian man living in Sao Paulo had recently visited Spain, Italy, Austria and Germany and returned to Sao Paulo with symptoms.
此外，尚有一位患者的新冠肺炎核酸检测呈阳性，目前正在接受复查，如复查确认，也将被确诊为新冠肺炎。
In addition, one patient who tested positive for Nucleic Acid (Nucleic Acid) in New Crown Pneumonia is currently under review and will be confirmed as New Crown Pneumonia if reviewed.
目前巴西疑似病例数量跃升至531例，此前累计已排除疑似病例为315例。
The number of suspected cases in Brazil has jumped to 531, after a cumulative total of 315 suspected cases have been cleared.
巴西先前确诊的两例新冠肺炎病例均属输入性病例，分别于2月26日和2月29日确诊，两人均为圣保罗居民，近期都曾到访意大利。
The two previously confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Brazil were imported and confirmed on 26 February and 29 February, respectively, both residents of São Paulo who had recently visited Italy.
法国0800【卢浮宫3月4日重新开放】卢浮宫去年接待的960万游客中，近四分之三来自国外。
The Louvre opened on March 4. Nearly three-quarters of the 9.6 million visitors to the Louvre last year came from abroad.
早前，法国政府宣布取消所有封闭环境中超过5000人的大型活动，除卢浮宫外，该禁令还会影响到法国数百家剧院和数千场文化活动。
Earlier, the French government announced the cancellation of all large-scale events involving more than 5,000 people in a closed environment. In addition to the Louvre, the ban would affect hundreds of theatres and thousands of cultural events in France.
0800【新增45例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计257例】据《巴黎人报》报道，法国报告新增45例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计报告257例。
According to Le Parisien, France has reported 45 new cases of diagnosed new crown pneumonia, with a cumulative total of 257 cases reported.
美国0830【确诊病例达153例 死亡11例】CNN援引美国疾控中心和各州及地方政府发布的消息，美国新冠肺炎确诊病例已达153例，死亡11例，治愈8例。
CNN quoted the CDC and state and local governments as saying there had been 153 confirmed cases of pneumonia, 11 cases of death and 8 cases of cure.
0800【洛杉矶地区进入紧急状态】据美国全国广播公司商业频道（CNBC）报道，洛杉矶地区官方宣布当地进入紧急状态，称他们在过去48小时内发现了6例新冠肺炎确诊病例。
Los Angeles state of emergency Los Angeles Officials in Los Angeles have declared a state of emergency, saying they have found six confirmed cases of pneumonia in the past 48 hours, the NBC commercial channel reported.
据报道，目前洛杉矶地区共有7人确诊新冠肺炎。
Seven people have been diagnosed with pneumonia in Los Angeles.
0800【美新冠肺炎确诊人数升至126例 死亡人数达11人】当地时间3月4日，全美共确诊126例新冠肺炎病例，位于13个州。
The number of confirmed cases of pneumonia rose to 126, bringing the total number of cases confirmed nationwide to 126, in 13 states, March 4, 2007.
死亡病例升至11例，8人来自在华盛顿州的同一个县，5人与西雅图郊区的一家养老院“生命护理中心”有关。
The death toll rose to 11, eight in the same county in Washington state and five in the Life Care Center, a nursing home in a Seattle suburb.
德国0800【德国累计确诊344例新冠肺炎病例】据德国《欧洲时报》德国当地时间3月4日20时公布的统计数据，截至3月4日20时，德国已累计确诊新冠肺炎患者344例，一天内确诊病例增加超过100例。
Germany confirmed 344 cases of new crown pneumonia on March 4 at 2000: 00 p.m. German daily The European Times reported a cumulative total of 344 cases of new crown pneumonia, an increase of more than 100 confirmed cases in a single day.
德国2020年汉诺威工业展推迟至7月举行阿尔及利亚0800【累计确诊17例，16例被同一人传染】据阿尔及利亚卫生、人口和医疗改革部3月4日消息，阿尔及利亚当日新增9例新冠肺炎确诊病例，境内已累计确诊17例。
The Hanover industrial exhibition in 2020 was postponed until July, when Algeria recorded a cumulative 17 cases of confirmed cases and 16 cases of infection by the same person. According to the Algerian Ministry of Health, Population and Health Reform, 9 new cases of new crown pneumonia were confirmed that day, with a cumulative total of 17 confirmed cases in Algeria.
除首例确诊病例外，其余16例均来自同一传染源。
All but the first confirmed cases came from the same source of infection.
消息显示，阿尔及利亚第二、第三确诊病例为一对居住在布里达省的母女。
According to the information received, the second and third confirmed cases in Algeria were a mother and daughter living in Brida province.
2月14日至21日期间，一名83岁法国籍亲属曾在其家中留宿，后因身体不适返回法国，在返回法国后病毒检测呈阳性。
Between 14 and 21 February, an 83-year-old relative of French nationality, who had stayed at his home, returned to France sick and tested positive for the virus upon his return to France.
这两名女性在3月1日被先后确诊，此后在阿确诊的14名感染患者均与这两名女性有过接触。
The two women were diagnosed on March 1, and all 14 infected patients diagnosed in Afghanistan have had contact with them since then.
印度0800【累计确诊29例病例其中包括16名意大利籍游客】印度媒体4日晚间报道，新德里附近卫星城古尔冈当晚确诊1名新冠肺炎病例，该病例近期刚从意大利度假归来，出现症状后就医，血液样本检测呈阳性，确诊感染。
Indian media reported Thursday night that a new crown pneumonia case was confirmed in Gurgaon, a satellite city near New Delhi, after returning from a recent holiday in Italy with symptoms and positive blood samples tested positive for infection.
当天早些时候，印度卫生部证实，4日当天印度共计出现包括15名意大利籍游客在内的23名确诊病例。
Earlier in the day, the Health Ministry confirmed a total of 23 confirmed cases in India on Thursday, including 15 Italian tourists.
总理莫迪和内政部长阿米特·沙阿等多名政要当天都呼吁民众不必恐慌，尽量减少聚集性活动，以防止疫情的大范围扩散。
Prime Minister Narendra Modi and Interior Minister Amite Shah appealed to the people the same day to avoid panic and minimize agglomeration in order to prevent the spread of the epidemic.
瑞典0800【瑞典新增新冠肺炎确诊病例22例累计确诊52例】当地时间3月4日晚，根据瑞典电视台（SVT）报道，瑞典一天内新增22例新冠肺炎确诊病例，目前瑞典已累计确诊病例52例。
Sweden confirmed 22 new cases of pneumonia on Monday night, Swedish television reported 22 new cases of pneumonia in a day, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 52 in Sweden.
西班牙0800【西班牙确诊新冠肺炎患者达193例首都马德里疫情最为严重】截至当地时间4日下午6点，西班牙确诊新冠肺炎患者达193例，其中首都马德里疫情依然最为严重，上升至76例。
Madrid has confirmed 193 cases of new crown pneumonia in Spain, with the capital, Madrid, still the most affected, up to 76 cases by 6 p.m. local time, the report said.
在这些患者中，有3例为儿童患者。
Of these patients, three were children.
目前西班牙政府还没有考虑关闭学校采取停课措措施。
The Spanish government has not yet considered closing schools for suspension.
世卫组织0800【中国境外新冠肺炎确诊共计12668例】根据世卫新冠肺炎情况每日报告，截至欧洲中部时间3月4日上午10时（北京时间17时），中国境外共76个国家确诊新冠肺炎12668例，死亡共计214例。
WHO 0800 Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia Outside China Daily Report: As of 10: 00 a.m. (17: 00 Beijing time) on March 4, 2009, 12,668 new cases and 214 deaths had been confirmed in 76 countries outside China, according to the WHO Daily Report on New Crown Pneumonia.
IMF0830【IMF和世行春季改开“虚拟”会议】多场相关活动在会议期间举办，吸引众多官员、记者和私营企业代表。
IMF0830 [The IMF and the World Bank switched to a "virtual" meeting in spring. Several events were held during the event, attracting a large number of officials, journalists, and private-sector representatives.
官方数据显示，与会者大约1万人。
According to official figures, there were about 10,000 participants.
按照公共卫生部门的建议，这类大型会议易出现聚集性病毒感染，应当尽量避免。
As recommended by the public health sector, such large meetings are prone to a concentrated virus infection and should be avoided to the extent possible.
0800【提供最高达500亿美元应对新冠肺炎疫情 】国际货币基金组织(IMF)当地时间4日宣布将提供最高达500亿美元资金协助成员国应对新冠肺炎疫情。
The International Monetary Fund announced Thursday that it will provide up to $50 billion to help member countries deal with the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown.
IMF总裁格奥尔基耶娃说，此次提供的500亿美元资金将通过紧急融资手段快速拨款给有需要的低收入国家和新兴经济体。
IMF Managing Director Sergei Georgieva says the $50 billion will be quickly allocated to low-income countries and emerging economies in need through emergency financing.
其中的100亿美元将通过无息贷款方式提供给最贫穷国家。
Of that amount, $10 billion will be made available to the poorest countries through interest-free loans.
